<P>A Sharp REBUKE From one of the PEOPLE called QUAKERS.</P>
<P>TO <HI>Henry Sacheverell,</HI> The HIGH-PRIEST of <HI>ANDREW</HI>'s <HI>HOLBOVRN.</HI></P>
